name: mixed_cb420y
source:
def mixed_cb420y(x, y):
    t1 = 1 / (1 + jnp.exp(-x))
    t2 = jnp.power(jnp.abs(t1), jnp.abs(y) % 3 + 1)
    t3 = jnp.min(t2)
    return t3

    f:f32[8] = div 1.0:f32[] e
    g:f32[8] = abs f
    h:f32[8] = abs b
    i:f32[8] = jit[
      name=remainder
      jaxpr={ lambda ; h:f32[8] j:i32[]. let
          k:f32[] = convert_element_type[new_dtype=float32 weak_type=False] j
          l:f32[8] = rem h k
          m:bool[8] = ne l 0.0:f32[]
          n:bool[8] = lt l 0.0:f32[]
          o:bool[] = lt k 0.0:f32[]
          p:bool[8] = ne n o
          q:bool[8] = and p m
          r:f32[8] = add l k
          i:f32[8] = select_n q l r
        in (i,) }
    ] h 3:i32[]
    s:f32[8] = add i 1.0:f32[]
    t:f32[8] = pow g s
    u:f32[] = reduce_min[axes=(0,)] t
  in (u,) }
